reviews.text: Absolute money making station .. it is a 'fine station' so what have they done ... put the machine in a place you can't see it on arrival and out absolutely no signs whatsoever anywhere advising there is a machine or where it is. First time users of this station are getting stung left right and centre from their innocent mistakes. Shame on you northern rail
Nice clean Station. Good links to all major towns

Station seating area is very dirty, pathway to platform 2 smells strongly of urine. Station does not have toilets or ticket buying facilities, no live details of train delays/train times. The station really lets down the surrounding area of patricroft.
Picturesque station with easy access to many local establishments..nothing is too much trouble for these slightly slow people
